author: KEXP
description: Minneapolis-based band @shesgreen dream in fuzz with airy shoegaze soundscapes and the ethereal vocals of lead singer Zofia Smith. With host DJ Cheryl Waters the band journey us through their discography with a live performance of "Mandy" and more.
title: she's green performs "Mandy" and more Live on KEXP
